notes: [Hospitalization from NMDH](https://cv.nmhealth.org/newsroom/). Hospitalization count is people in New Mexico hospitals: it includes people who tested positive out of state but are hospitalized in New Mexico, and excludes New Mexicans who tested positive in state and transferred to a hospital out of state. As of April 27, New Mexico is reporting people tested. On 5/28 NM reported ~1100 less tests than the day before. We're unsure of the reason.
